release_note: We fixed a few bugs in version 5.19.3: The scrolling that was lagging when there were offline songs in a list was fixed. The percentage of vocal match is displayed again even when it s below 90

Don t let the winter bring you down and sing with KaraFun 5.19.2 : KaraFun went through quite the makeover to make your experience more fun! We made some improvements to make the interface clearer and nicer to the eye: the locked songs covers are now grey instead of pink and the explicit tag was replaced with a standard E . The in queue and recently played icons were also changed. The song menu was also reworked to make it more user friendly. Finally we fixed a few minor bugs.

For this new version 5.18.2 we fixed a communication issue that prevented some users from immediately using their newly purchased subscription.

Back to school and back to singing with KaraFun 5.18.1! The KaraFun tracks can now be played with Airplay compatible audio devices. To sing anywhere whenever you want! You can now choose your audio output directly from the app. The transitions between songs were improved. The bug that made the app freeze when clicking on Manage subscription was fixed.

Summer is here and with it some hot news from KaraFun 5.18.0! We reworked the keyboard shortcuts and shortcut list it should now be more clear and identical to the macOS version. The playlist creation process was improved Several issues tied to songs Drag Drop were fixed. Mainly related to the options not being copied properly Other various bugs were fixed We made several minor interface improvements. iPad The issue causing favorites songs to be re selected is fixed.

Sun is up and changes are ahead with version 5.17.0! You can now purchase your pro subscription via the app and change your pro settings without having to go to our website: add your own logo activate the permanent URL and the extended catalog. The new version allows you to delete songs in your history or even clear it out completely. The design was improved and made more accessible. It is now possible to directly drag and drop songs from a song list KaraFun playlist personalized playlist history etc. to the queue!

Spring is finally here and so is KaraFun 5.16.0 Access your community files from a new dedicated section on the app. A search field was added in the history so that you can search by title artist singer name or year. You can now also search by singer name in your playlists. The bug that prevented the background music from showing in the settings was fixed.

Days are getting longer... More time to sing with KaraFun 5.15.5! The key and tempo are now displayed correctly when the lyrics are full screen. The black screen bug the renderer being randomly black is fixed. We fixed other small bugs. The bug that prevented songs from starting in the right key was fixed.

Days are getting longer... More time to sing with KaraFun 5.15.4! The key and tempo are now displayed correctly when the lyrics are full screen. The black screen bug the renderer being randomly black is fixed. We fixed other small bugs.

Bring sunshine to your heart with KaraFun 5.15.2! It is not possible to access the lyrics of an explicit song if parental control is on. Better safe than sorry! Little bugs were fixed on the sign in and log in page: you will not be able to choose a birthdate in the future anymore and you will be advised when you re trying to type the wrong login information. Bye bye iOS 14! Please note that this OS will not be supported in the new version.

Bring sunshine to your heart with KaraFun 5.15.2! It is not possible to access the lyrics of an explicit song if parental control is on. Better safe than sorry! Little bugs were fixed on the sign in and log in page: you will not be able to choose a birthdate in the future anymore and you will be advised when you re trying to type the wrong login information. Bye bye iOS 14! Please note that this OS will not be supported in the new version.

Version 5.15 gets new improvements with version 5.15.1! Your preferences are now saved when you copy a song from a playlist or the queue to another playlist. The lead voices are not reversed anymore in duets.

Survive through winter with KaraFun 5.15.0! The history feature is improved: songs are added immediately when they start. No need for them to reach 45 seconds! You cannot add more than 999 songs to the queue anymore: this should prevent loading issues. The app is globally prettier and smoother.

Hohoho Santa Claus is coming to town and he s not empty handed! Discover KaraFun 5.14.6. The play now function was improved: the first song in the queue is not deleted anymore if it has not started yet but it is pushed to second place. No need to search for the song again if a singer is late! The duration of the queue is calculated with more precision and changes along with the song currently played. The app is smoother in general and minor bugs were fixed.

Leaves attire themselves in a thousand colors and KaraFun puts on a new version: 5.14.3 The transition between two songs was improved. It is now possible to sort your songs in decreasing order. The loading bug that could happened when moving forward or backwards on the progression bar was fixed.

Back to school and back to singing! Welcome to version 5.14.2! The app becomes more accessible: you can now deactivate the karaoke animated background and use a plain black background. From now on the remote works for all users even those without a subscription: a good way to try it out before subscribing! We added some improvements including in the song options and the settings.

No vacation for KaraFun: say welcome to version 5.14! The app becomes more accessible: you can now deactivate the karaoke animated background and use a plain black background. From now on the remote works for all users even those without a subscription: a good way to try it out before subscribing! We added some improvements including in the song options and the settings.

No vacation for KaraFun: say welcome to version 5.14! The app becomes more accessible: you can now deactivate the karaoke animated background and use a plain black background. From now on the remote works for all users even those without a subscription: a good way to try it out before subscribing! We added some improvements including in the song options and the settings.

Make your summer even brighter with KaraFun 5.13! You rocked it a few weeks ago and you d like to sing those songs again Your tracks are now sorted by date in your history. Find the list will take a few seconds only! The fading is back when you go from one song to the other so that there is no blank in the sound nor in the mood! The app is globally smoother and nicer looking.

Find your song match and become the superstar you always were with version 5.12.0! Do you find it hard to find the right song for your voice Are you tired of starting a song and realizing it s too low or too high Discover KaraFun s new feature: Vocal Match. Record your voice to find the perfect songs for you!
Go even further with 5.11.2! Managing your relationship with KaraFun becomes easier! You can now cancel your subscription directly from the app. Minor bugs were fixed.
5.11.1: version 5.11.0 but better The offline search is more comprehensible Minor bugs were fixed

Days are getting longer and KaraFun keeps on getting better with version 5.11! Songs are now stored in your history with their modifications of key tempo and volume. No more time spent trying to remember your settings. Find your tracks the way you sang them and add them to your playlist or your queue! You can also add a song to a playlist from another playlist with all modifications saved. The design of the app was improved. We want KaraFun to be as much of a treat for your eyes as it is for your ears!

KaraFun 5.10.0 is looking better than ever! More colors new banners never underestimate a little makeover. Upgrade to a Monthly Subscription directly from the app: get the most out of KaraFun and access all features in just a couple clicks! Stay up to date: starting with this version KaraFun no longer supports iOS 13 and requires a minimum of iOS 14. Never sing the same song twice! You can visually track the songs you ve already played in your session. Minor fixes and a lot of improvements under the hood.

All I want for 2022 is version 5.9! The search is enriched: look for one thing and find not only songs but artists playlists suggestions Try it out with New Year and see what 2022 brings! The songs are loading faster: there is always time for one more!

Winter is coming but singing keeps you warm with KaraFun 5.8! You could already sort your playlists by title artist or date. You can now sort your favorite and offline lists as well! Lose no time it s party time! available on iOS15 and up We fixed a few minor bugs.

Version 5.7 loses the mask for Halloween! What to expect: Your my songs tab has got a new interface. It s prettier and also adapts better to the use of KaraFun on iPad. You will now get a warning when you modify your song options in a playlist while being offline: no more bad surprises when you discover your preferences were not saved! Apart from that a few minor bugs were fixed and the general interface was improved. It s time to dress up with your scariest costumes and to launch our special Halloween karaoke playlist!

Version 5.6 is here! What s improved: The app opens now twice as quickly open it and sing! For the iPad experts know that KaraFun now allows the use of the multi window feature. What s fixed: iPadOS 15 users can now add songs to their playlists again. No more random black screens when your external screen is unplugged

Version 5.6 is here! What s improved: The app opens now twice as quickly open it and sing! For the iPad experts know that KaraFun now allows the use of the multi window feature. What s fixed: iPadOS 15 users can now add songs to their playlists again. No more random black screens when your external screen is unplugged

KaraFun 5.5.0 is here and we have news for you! You can use the search bar in your playlists and your favorites! If you are using our catalog in the offline mode you can now search and find every song you need. Organizing your playlists is more intuitive as you don t need to enter the edit mode anymore you can just drag and drop the song easier than ever! If you can t find the karaoke song you are looking for after searching for it this version allows you to request it directly in the App: go in Settings and click Suggest a song .

Release note 5.4.0 EN The major updates of this version: The lyrics screen may look the same but we ve made some improvements: try it yourself and enjoy the sleekness! The buttons react better to touch the queue is more user friendly and transitions and animations are smoother Small details really do make all the difference! Good news for our iPad lovers: you will now be able to see lyrics even better while the lyrics screen is minimized meaning you can keep on singing while looking for the next song! We ve also tackled some minor bugs: Our home page display is more fluid the remote control is steadier and overlapping windows are now resolved we re always aiming for perfection and to bring you the best karaoke experience ever! Happy singing!

KaraFun 5.3.0 is here with some surprises we re sure you ll like! What to expect: We know you ve been waiting for them PERSONALIZED PLAYLISTS! That means you can sort your songs by singer by genre whatever and however you want! And think big there s no limit to the number of playlists nor songs you can add. You can save the key and tempo of your tracks you can even choose to sync them automatically for offline use. No time wasted looking for your songs...it s singtime! Change the volume of each song from the queue and also the key and tempo. You ll be all set when the mic is passed to you! Changes to the Parental Control Feature .. explicit songs will appear in the song list but you won t be able to add them to the queue. What s improved: Song suggestions are proposed throughout your karaoke session based on what you re singing at the moment more inspiration more singing more fun! The keyboard will disappear when you click on a song during a search. And it will not hide your lyrics anymore if you decide to play the song right away!

New update Version 5.2.2! We re working on some super cool new features but before we release that version we wanted to make sure that we bring you the most bug free version possible. Pretty important we d say so make sure to update to get the most stable version possible!

Check out our newest version of the KaraFun App! Here s what to keep your eyes and ears open for: Return of 10 10 to fast forward or rewind a song Improved player icons in portrait mode Improved overall performance of the App Recent search list Correction of offline song synchronization and Top Songs Minor bug fixes Warm up the microphones KaraFun is here! And just as a reminder: Introducing KaraFun version 5.0. This one s a doozy hold on to your microphones because we re going to make you a star right in your very own living room! Here s what you ll find: A redesigned home page to access all the new tunes even faster. Screen in portrait mode no more craning your neck each time you change screen direction. More info screen conforms to tactile navigation and in just a tap you can easily access all of the features. A new easier way to manage the volume. Volume settings are automatically saved based on the last song played. Set the default volume of the background music directly from the main screen. For Business Users: control the volume of sound output directly from the application. And there s more! MORE FREE SONGS! If you re still on the fence about testing the app take advantage of our growing list of free songs... you re sure to find ones you ll love! We re hard at work at KaraFun to make your singing experience even better so never hesitate to share your thoughts and comments with us or give us a rating on the App Store!

Here comes the sun and with it comes a new change for KaraFun iOS 4.7.2! Double Tap on the full screen to fast forward or rewind to your favorite part of the song.
Here comes the sun and with it come some new changes for KaraFun iOS 4.7.1! Features exclusively for KaraFun Business users. Minor fixes and improvements.

365 new days to sing.... go on grab KaraFun our most recent version and bring on 2019! Here s what you ll find in 4.7.0: Strong Password Suggestions keeping you super secure in the new year! Pro users can opt to hide community files. Fixed: Background music now plays after logging out and back in.

A fond farewell to iOS 9 on KaraFun! A well deserved retirement often brings new beginnings! Goodbye as well to the iOS 12 pop up crash and hello to newly designed navigation icons! Voilà...a quick but very welcomed update!

Bringing you some extra rays of sunshine during the summer months in version 4.5.0. On the docket: NEW Ask singer s name when adding to queue can now be activated from the settings page under Playback or Remote Control. Say my name say my name! Arabic characters Yep they re now supported leaving you saying shukran. Non latin languages are supported in the scrolling banner feature for pro users. FIXED Minor bug fixes.
Last update correction: The background music of Karafun dashed only once in the starting up of the application then it kept silent for ever. It is now corrected!

4.4.4! Triple digits a sign of good things to come. And that s exactly what this version brings! Fixed Background music no longer overtakes the song your trying to sing. Mic hog much ! Background music will play even when an external screen is hooked up. The message Your song queue is empty is only displayed now when your queue really is completely and entirely empty. Scrolling banner: No more weird looking characters for accents and letters in various languages.

Resolutions shmesolutions KaraFun iOS is consistently bettering itself. In 4.4.3 you ll find a few fixes and improvements. Happy singing in 2018! New KaraFun went back to night school and buffed up on Turkish Polish Romanian Russian and Korean and will soon be expanding its karaoke catalog! Pro users: Singer management is getting smarter and will only display the number of singers and next songs that match the session time. Fixed Cheeeese! No more freezes when you send photos from the remote feature. Click click click! That pesky audio click heard at the beginning of each song has gone and clicked for its last time. Simple calculations don t scare us anymore. We ve fixed a crash that happened when searching digits with letters. Like what you see Don t hesitate to show us some lovin on the App Store or share with a friend!
Tis the season to be singing fa la la la la! A couple quick adjustments to make the holidays brighter. Improvements Use with iOS 9 Fixed Naughty bugs that caused rare crashes
Tis the season to be singing fa la la la la! A couple quick adjustments to make the holidays brighter. Improvements Use with iOS 9 Fixed Naughty bugs that caused rare crashes

Our iOS team s checklist for version 4.4.0 note the nifty new features for pro users! NEW iOS11 and iPhone X compatible check! Vocals volume key and tempo displayed without needing to tap the Player screen check! NEW FOR PRO SESSION USERS Remote permissions reset with each new session check! Volumes key and tempo no longer reset with each new session check! Each session display only the number of songs in queue that correspond to the remaining time in a session check! Singer Management: Display the next 5 singers scrolling across the top of the Player screen along with custom message possibility check!

Today s iOS update 4.3.0 is brought to you by Tom and Vincent working hard to make sure your karaoke nights are bug free and chock full of singing. New Features Song Community Reporting: Report any community songs uploaded by members that are poor quality out of sync etc. Multiple Background Musics: Select more than one background musics to play between karaoke videos and randomly play them. Do the Shuffle! Improvements Optimized Search: Better stronger faster results. Improved suggestions on the fullscreen player when idle Pro user adjustments: Disabling and resetting of volume sliders key and tempo when a session ends. Remote Feature Makeover: User experience and your comments forced us to take a look in the mirror and adjust. Fixed: Sync Songs Freeze: Bug causing app to freeze when syncing songs in offline mode. Chilly! Password Length: Now you can login even with your loooooong password. Minor bug fixes

Question: What do you get when some rare bugs and the KaraFun dev team cross paths on their way to a Friday night karaoke Answer: Here s the rundown: Fixed: Background music that didn t play when it was supposed to. Fixed: Offline syncing of the Top Songs actually synced what it wanted. We set it straight. Fixed: Mono Stereo surround sound only playing the left audio. Time to hook up the surround sound! Rollback: Start in Pause mode ALWAYS starts a song in pause. No exceptions!

A KaraFun Love Poem Roses are red Violets are blue Lots of got new features specially for you! So take the mic let s croon together We ll sing on forever and ever! New Features Sync top songs offline: Love at first sight you can now see how much space you re using when you sync the top songs offline. Play Now: Even if Start in pause is activated tapping on Play now will start the song. Auto lock: Breakups are hard. That s why we got rid of automatic lock when you re hooking up with a screen on KaraFun. New Pro Features Password protected settings! Hide My songs favorites offline and history so only you can see and access them. Set a length of session time and KaraFun will be blocked automatically when the times up. We re Smitten! Fixed iPhone 7 users: Went through a bit of a rough patch but we fixed the funky noises and lags. Remote control users: Lots of performance improvements and no more session breakups we re going steady now. Logging in with email and username: The end of trying to log in with email or username and getting blocked. We dumped it. Can our team get a little lovin Be our Valentine with a review on the App Store or on the KaraFun Facebook page!

Our app has feasted over a Bugkin Pie and is now stronger for the winter! iPhone 7 owners rejoice: we re back to normal and the pesky bug that was causing sound issues is now gone. Take the tree out bake the sugar cookies plug the microphones in: let s get singing!

Cause it s witchcraft wicked witchcraft. A couple of fixes from our dev magicians that quickly resolved the following: Fixed: Bug causing the lead vocals to play even when set to zero on previously played songs. Fixed: Lags and skips when playing certain songs. And now back to the most recent changes . Trick or Treat Play a beat Make sure it s on KaraFun 4.1 so sweet! This is no hocus pocus KaraFun has added and improved: Remote control: Singers can now search for songs and control the Queue directly from their smartphone and tablets. It s a kinda magic! Play Now: Back from the dead your cries were loud and clear and you ll notice the return of the Play Now button. It can be found on the song page after tapping on any song. Queue Count and Timing: Now you see the number of songs in your Queue and the time to sing them all. Song Info: Now making it s appearance in the Queue menu. Pro users: Sync the 10k and 20k most popular songs faster than you can say Boo and add your logo to have it appear instantly. Horror of all horrors KaraFun had to fix a few things: The inexplicable sorcery that caused the volume controls to automatically adjust back to zero. The iPhone 7 bug that made some pretty spooky sounds. Song suggestions that vanished into thin air have reappeared and you can see them on the song page. Mystery solved and resolved! Other frightful small bugs. Feedback Get in touch with us via www.karafun.com. Or leave us a note on the App Store.

Well gosh darn it a couple of slimy little bugs got past us. Our team worked night and day to squash them in their tracks. Fixed: A crash caused when playing songs from your queue that had been added before making the update. Fixed: Hooking up your device to an external screen displayed the app in its full glory rather than just the Player with video and text. Well that s was embarrassing! Fixed: Updating the catalog required that you update it again. And again. And again. And in case you missed the super duper changes from last week: Makeover: a set of changes that are intended to make something more attractive Extreme makeover: a set of changes in an effort to transform something and make dreams come true. We shot for an extreme makeover with this one. Introducing the new the improved the beautiful KaraFun Version 4.0! New Features Redesigned Interface: New layout useful buttons and swipes to add a song to the Queue or Offline This version is quite the head turner! Background Music: Zen or funk no more awkward silences in between songs. Community Imports: Recall our snazzy Mac feature that allows you to upload your files to share with others Well now they can also be found on your iPhone and iPad. Skip to the Next Singer: Activate this feature and when the words are done your singing turn is too. Next... Version 3.5 brings some welcome changes! Improvements: We took our Gingko pills and the memory s been optimized. Who s next Edit singer info or change song order right up until the song starts playing. A sole song that is added to the queue still plays right away even if START IN PAUSE mode is enabled. Fixed: iCloud was wanting to get in on the action too but we ve made it so only certain songs remain synced on your device. Smile! No more unhappy faces when trying to add emojis to Singer Name. : Play it again Sam. Should connection be lost we pick it up right where you left off. The sky s the limit up to 1000 at least! Offline syncing doesn t get stuck anymore! Had a case of the shakes when playing some songs that caused loading to wiggle and move! We shook it off.

30 days makes 720 hours makes 43 200 minutes. However you say it that s a lot of time available for you to sing your heart out on your iPhone and iPad. One month passes are now possible via your iPad and iPhone. Take that weekly pass! Not to deflect from this awesome news but that isn t all. Our dev team worked day in and day out to make other improvements that will help songs play better offline mode run smoother and account information more personal. Stronger than yesterday here are some IMPROVEMENTS: Jitters be gone! We optimized performance to make playing a karaoke song smoother. Keyboard closes automatically after searching finding and clicking on that perfect song. Our offline mode notification got a pretty little makeover or maybe we should call it a makeunder . We now save your played songs in History even longer for easy reference after your party. Bring it up bring it up 8 hours to 16! Bugs be gone we FIXED the following: Those pesky volume sliders on iPad are easier to manoeuvre as is the possibility to enlarge the video window when it is minimized. That search field that didn t make searching so easy on your iPad we ve tackled that.

Kanye said it Nothing that don t kill me can only make me stronger. This 3.3.0 release is bigger stronger and bug free er than ever! After a long hard look in the mirror and some gentle nudges from our users we ve made some necessary changes to our karaoke lifestyle: Free from the flab that weighed us down we ve gutted the code and replaced it with a leaner and meaner one fortified memory and faster everything! . Help us help you meet your karaoke goals. We ve got a new profile section all buffed up with any information about you and your subscription. Longterm pro We ve upped our game with access to never before released content. Think KaraFun deserves a gold medal Give us access to the winners podium with a five star rating. Think otherwise Come talk to us we re here for you.
What s new 2016 s got a lot going musically and to get you ready for a year of singing we re always making improvements and fixing the minor bugs. Happy Singing!
